Text: Why is this a puzzle? It is a PDF Book about how to use SolidWorks 2010 and the companion files used in the examples in the book! SolidWorks uses parametric design to create 3d models.

I hate to state the obvious, but if you do not know what SolidWorks is, or know what this book is, you don't need it.

The SolidWorks 2010 Bible is a tutorial and training book on how to use the engineering CAD software SolidWorks 2010. This particular torrent features the ebook and supplementary training files.

Now that SolidWorks 2011 is out I hope the 2011 Bible is right around the corner.
